<paragraph blockId="20.[189,1399,1624,1687]" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">A yellow species with a yellow occiput and a yellow scutum, but a black scutellum and metanotum. Metapleuron yellow. The tip of the hypopleuron (meron) above hind coxae with a black spot.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
